graph TD
    classDef human fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#2e7d32,stroke-width:2px
    classDef primary fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1565c0,stroke-width:2px
    classDef subagent fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#e65100,stroke-width:1px
    classDef skill fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#7b1fa2,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray:5 5
    classDef decision fill:#fff8e1,stroke:#f9a825,stroke-width:2px
    classDef terminal fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#c62828,stroke-width:2px

    Start((Start)) --> HasSpecRepo{Has specrepo/ and AGENTS.md?}
    HasSpecRepo -->|No| Bootstrap[Ask @specrepo-bootstrapper]:::primary
    HasSpecRepo -->|Yes| RequestAuthor

    Bootstrap --> BootstrapOut[Generate specrepo docs/templates/specs and root AGENTS.md]:::primary
    BootstrapOut --> RequestAuthor

    subgraph RequestPhase[Request -> Proposal -> Approval]
        RequestAuthor[Call @request-author]:::primary
        RequestSkill[Load specrepo-request]:::skill
        SpecReviewer[Delegate to @spec-reviewer]:::subagent
        ProposalSkill[Load specrepo-proposal]:::skill
        ArchApprover[Delegate to @architecture-approver]:::subagent
        ApprovalSkill[Load specrepo-approval]:::skill
        ApprovalResult{Approval result}:::decision

        RequestAuthor --> RequestSkill
        RequestSkill --> SpecReviewer
        SpecReviewer --> ProposalSkill
        ProposalSkill --> ArchApprover
        ArchApprover --> ApprovalSkill
        ApprovalSkill --> ApprovalResult
    end

    ApprovalResult -->|approve: approval record created| HumanReview
    ApprovalResult -->|revise / reject| StopRev((Stop)):::terminal

    subgraph HumanGate[Human Review]
        HumanReview{Review proposal and approval}:::human
        Satisfied{Satisfied?}:::decision
        HumanReview --> Satisfied
    end

    Satisfied -->|Yes: call @spec-coder| SpecCoder
    Satisfied -->|No: stop| StopImpl((Stop)):::terminal

    subgraph ImplPhase[Implementation -> Verification -> Test Review]
        SpecCoder[Call @spec-coder]:::primary
        NeedImplReview{Implementation review exists?}:::decision
        ImplReview[Delegate to @implementation-reviewer]:::subagent
        ImplReviewSkill[Load specrepo-implementation-review]:::skill
        ImplGate{Proceed?}:::decision
        Implement[Implement approved scope]:::primary
        UpdateSpecs[Update baseline specs if behavior changed]:::primary
        VerifySkill[Load specrepo-verification]:::skill
        Verify[Run approved verification]:::primary
        TestReviewer[Delegate to @test-reviewer]:::subagent
        TestReviewSkill[Load specrepo-verification]:::skill
        TestResult{Test review result}:::decision
        FixTests[Fix tests or implementation within approved scope]:::primary
        AutocommitSkill[Load specrepo-autocommit]:::skill
        Autocommit[Call specrepo-autocommit tool]:::primary

        SpecCoder --> NeedImplReview
        NeedImplReview -->|No| ImplReview
        NeedImplReview -->|Yes| Implement
        ImplReview --> ImplReviewSkill
        ImplReviewSkill --> ImplGate
        ImplGate -->|Proceed| Implement
        ImplGate -->|Stop for revised architecture| StopArch((Stop)):::terminal
        Implement --> UpdateSpecs
        UpdateSpecs --> VerifySkill
        VerifySkill --> Verify
        Verify -->|passed| TestReviewer
        Verify -->|failed / skipped / cannot run| StopVerify((Stop)):::terminal
        TestReviewer --> TestReviewSkill
        TestReviewSkill --> TestResult
        TestResult -->|pass| AutocommitSkill
        TestResult -->|needs more tests| FixTests
        FixTests --> VerifySkill
        TestResult -->|blocked| StopBlock((Stop)):::terminal
        AutocommitSkill --> Autocommit
    end

    Autocommit --> FinalReview

    subgraph MergePhase[Final Review]
        FinalReview[Review summary and git diff]:::human
        Merge{Ready to merge?}:::decision
        FinalMerge((Merge)):::terminal

        FinalReview --> Merge
        Merge -->|Yes| FinalMerge
        Merge -->|No| Reject((Do not merge)):::terminal
    end

    StopImpl -.->|refine request| RequestAuthor
    StopRev -.->|clarify request| RequestAuthor
    StopArch -.->|revise architecture| SpecReviewer
